Borough Council external works to premises in Bletchingley, Surrey.
The Peabody Trust has awarded three contracts with a total value of Pounds
912,000. They cover a 52-week maintenance contract; Phase 2 of refurbishment
works on the Peabody Estate and refurbishment at Chapter Court in West
Bridge Road.
A contract has also been awarded to the Mansell Group by Glaxo, valued at
Pounds 3.2m, for refurbishment works to premises at Greenford.
