<HEADLINE>
FT  16 SEP 92 / UK Company News: FT-SE Eurotrack 100 Index
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The FT-SE Eurotrack steering committee has agreed to make the following
changes to the FT-SE Eurotrack 100 Index constituent list with effect from
September 21.
