         DIRECT INVESTMENT - % change over previous year
 ------------------------------------------------------------------
Recipient:       Asia (exc   Europe   N America   Japan   World
                    Japan)
 ------------------------------------------------------------------
Japan              -15.8     -34.4      -30.8        -    -26.9
US                 +36.5     -62.9          -    -23.4    -51.6
 ------------------------------------------------------------------
